Divalicious Mrs India Universe ( DELHI NCR )  We’re excited to announce a brand new avatar of the Divalicious Mrs. India Universe beauty contest!
This season, we are launching State-Level Beauty Contests across India.

Winners from each state will receive a Direct Entry to the Divalicious Mrs. India Universe 2026 (National Level) beauty contest!

There will be two age categories:
Classic: 21 to 35 years
Platinum: 35+ to 48 years

So what are you waiting for?
Click the link below, fill out the form, and make your state proud by representing it on the National Stage.
Let your journey to the crown begin today!

To apply . www.mrsuniverseorg.com
